descp2: str, list or tuple of str, default=None Attribute name(s) given as string or a list/tuple of strings Eg.: ``["coef_", "estimator_", ...], "coef_"`` If `None`, `estimator` is considered fitted if there exist an attribute that ends with a underscore and does not start with double underscore.
